<title>sbḥwh</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 sbĩḥwhu wmjĩdwh wạrfʿwạ ạsmahu ạlʿẓym
 bhutạfiⁿ mlĩkwh mʿ ṣfwfi ạlsmạỷyyn
 ạlmsyḥu qạm bạlḥqyqẗi qd qạm
 muḥaṭĩmạaⁿ qwy̱ ạlsẖyṭạn wsạḥqa ạlmwti bsulṭạn
 qdĩmwạ lhu ạlsũjwd ạlạ̹lhu ạlḥqũ ạlạ̉myn
 man fdạnạ wkẖlãṣnạ bdmhi ạlzky ạltẖmyn
 ạ̹nsẖdwạ ạ̉ḥly̱ ạlạ̉ngẖạm rnĩmwạ lmliknạ ạlmsyḥ
 fhw wḥdh mustḥq klã ạ̹krạmiⁿ wtsbyḥ
 hạ dẖbyḥẗa sẖukry lh qd ạ̉qạmnạ bqyạmtih
 wrfaʿnạ fwqa klĩ ḍʿf wạ̉ʿṭạnạ mn qwtih</lyrics>
</song>